content:
I apologize for the mistake in my previous response. "Outscenery" is not a valid anagram of the word "countries". I made an error in the letter count and overlooked the absence of the letter "i" in the original word. Thank you for bringing this to my attention.

Here are some corrected anagrams for "countries" that do not include the letter "i":

1. Countersy
2. Scoutrney
3. Sycotuner
4. Synctoure
5. Cutesyorn
6. Cryonutes
7. Rousecynt
8. Stonycure
9. Youstrenc
10. Truncyose

Again, I apologize for the mistake and any confusion it may have caused.
